2014年，希雅为她的第六张录音室专辑《[[一千种恐惧|一千种恐惧]]》录制了一首独唱版的〈勇者之心〉。<ref>{{cite AV media notes|title=[[1000_Forms_of_Fear|1000 Forms of Fear]]|others=[[Sia_(musician)|Sia]]|publisher=[[RCA_Records|RCA]]/Monkey Puzzle|type=liner notes}}</ref>2015年1月9日歌曲由RCA唱片作为专辑中的第三首单曲发行。<ref name="Airplay" />来自The A.V. Club的Annie Zaleski将〈勇者之心〉形容為「驚人的力量民谣」<ref name="AVClub">{{cite web|title=Accidental pop songwriter Sia doesn't quite reclaim solo career momemtum|url=http://www.avclub.com/review/accidental-pop-songwriter-sia-doesnt-quite-reclaim-206353|accessdate=2015-01-24|date=2014-07-08|last=Zaleski|first=Annie|work=[[The_A.V._Club|The A.V. Club]]|archive-date=2015-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150520201059/http://www.avclub.com/review/accidental-pop-songwriter-sia-doesnt-quite-reclaim-206353|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而AllMusic的Heather Phares则将这首歌与〈[[水晶吊灯_(歌曲)|水晶吊燈]]〉、〈針尖之眼〉一起选为专辑中的三大亮点之一。<ref>{{cite web|title=1000 Forms of Fear – Sia {{!}} Songs, Reviews, Credits, Awards|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/1000-forms-of-fear-mw0002680594|accessdate=2015-01-09|last=Phares|first=Heather|publisher=[[AllMusic|AllMusic]]|archive-date=2015-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150511071908/http://www.allmusic.com/album/1000-forms-of-fear-mw0002680594|dead-url=no}}</ref>来自Fact的Aimee Cliff将其命名为 "只有希雅才能真正演繹为希雅写的（而不是由希雅写的）歌曲的一大例子"。<ref name="Fact">{{cite web|title=1000 Forms of Fear – FACT magazine|url=http://www.factmag.com/2014/07/16/1000-forms-of-fear/|accessdate=2015-01-09|date=2014-07-16|last=Cliff|first=Aimee|work=[[Fact_(UK_magazine)|Fact]]|archive-date=2015-03-25|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6XHbM4GXJ?url=http://www.factmag.com/2014/07/16/1000-forms-of-fear/|dead-url=no}}</ref>《1000 Forms of Fear》的豪华版包括了这首歌的钢琴版。

在意大利，〈勇者之心〉于2015年1月9日派至当代热门电台。<ref name="Airplay" />〈勇者之心〉在2015年1月19日发行的ARIA单曲榜，排名第8。<ref>{{cite web|title=ARIA Australian Top 50 Singles Chart|url=http://ariacharts.com.au/chart/singles|accessdate=2015-01-24|publisher=[[ARIA_Charts|ARIA Charts]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140322200515/http://ariacharts.com.au/chart/singles|archivedate=2014-03-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>次周，这首歌升至第5名。<ref name="AuPeak" />[[澳大利亚唱片业协会|澳大利亚唱片业协会]]对其頒發3×白金认证，表示在澳大利亚的出货量超过21万张。<ref name="ariacert" /><ref>{{cite web|title=International Certified Awards|url=http://ifpi.org/content/library/international-award-levels.pdf|accessdate=2014-05-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140328112251/http://ifpi.org/content/library/international-award-levels.pdf|archivedate=2014-03-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>在美国，〈勇者之心〉在2015年1月24日[[告示牌百强单曲榜|《公告牌》百強單曲榜]]上首次出現，排名第17位，成为当周的「热門首发」。<ref>{{cite web|title=Hot 100 Chart Moves: Video Controversy Sends Sia's 'Elastic Heart' to No. 17 Debut|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6443523/hot-100-chart-moves-sia-video-controversy|accessdate=2015-01-24|date=2015-01-16|last=Trust|first=Gary|work=Billboard|archive-date=2016-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160412134618/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6443523/hot-100-chart-moves-sia-video-controversy|dead-url=no}}</ref>随后，这首歌在美国的销量和流媒体综合销量达到200万张，获得双白金认证。<ref name="RIAA">{{Cite web |url=http://www.riaa.com/goldandplatinumdata.php?content_selector=gold-platinum-searchable-database |title=RIAA's Gold and Platinum Program |accessdate=2020-11-21 |archive-date=2016-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160103185214/http://www.riaa.com/goldandplatinumdata.php?content_selector=gold-platinum-searchable-database |dead-url=no }}</ref>在英国，该单曲于2015年4月5日在[[英國單曲排行榜|英国单曲榜]]上名列第10位，此后获得[[英国唱片业协会|英国唱片业协会]]的双白金认证。<ref name="UKSolo" /><ref name="bpi" />

